so what we did is we went to the local Target

00:01:49.220 --> 00:01:53.380
in downtown Chicago and we bought this little
egg timer. It was just a couple bucks, we

00:01:53.380 --> 00:01:58.180
ripped off the base so it would lay flat,
and then we bought some sticky tack. Now what

00:01:58.180 --> 00:02:03.810
we did with this sticky tack is we merely
pushed it down onto the top of the egg timer,

00:02:03.810 --> 00:02:08.500
